text: Taylor Karl Gunman (born 14 March 1991 in Takapuna) is a New Zealand cyclist who last rode for . He won the 2015 UCI Oceania Tour following his victory in the Oceania Continental Championships road race. ==Major results== ;2009 : 1st Stage 3 Tour of Northland : 2nd Tour de l'Abitibi ;2010 : 1st Stage 2 Tour of Northland ;2011 : 3rd REV Classic ;2013 : 2nd Overall Tour of Southland ::1st Prologue (TTT) & Stage 4 : 3rd Time trial, National Under–23 Road Championships ;2014 : 1st 20px Time trial, National Road Championships : 1st Prologue (TTT) Tour of Southland ;2015 : 1st 20px Road race, Oceania Road Championships : 1st 20px Overall New Zealand Cycle Classic ;2016 : 3rd REV Classic ==References== ==External links== * Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:New Zealand male cyclists Category:People from Auckland
